text: Nidia is a female given name that may refer to professional wrestler Nidia Guenard or another notable person listed below: *Nidia Bustos Nicaraguan director *Nidia Morrell (born 1953), Argentine astronomer *Nidia Muñoz (born 1991), Cuban taekwondoist *Nidia María Jiménez Vásquez Costa Rican politician *Nidia Vílchez (born 1964), Peruvian politician ==See also== Category:Feminine given names
title: Nidia (given name)
